      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Experience automotive excellence with this impeccably maintained vehicle, presented in true showroom condition. Every detail, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine, smoke-free interior, reflects a standard of care rarely seen on the secondary market. This is a turnkey opportunity for the discerning driver who demands uncompromising quality and mechanical integrity. Fully inspected and detailed to perfection, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of its class and offers an unparalleled driving experience.",
